n-list\" data-id=\"196e507\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-list.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"elementor-icon-list-items elementor-inline-items\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item elementor-inline-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"tel:+17815201982\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"remixicon ri-phone-fill\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">+17815201982<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-1a4a5ed5 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default exad-glass-effect-no exad-sticky-section-no elementor-invisible\" data-id=\"1a4a5ed5\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;fadeIn&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-background-overlay\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-2f25244c exad-glass-effect-no exad-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"2f25244c\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0b8c3cb exad-sticky-section-no exad-glass-effect-no elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0b8c3cb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Our story begins with a dream. In 2016, our founder, <strong>Rebbert de Oliveira<\/strong>, a Brazilian immigrant who studied Civil Engineering, arrived in the United States determined to build a new life. Starting from the ground up\u2014working as a carpenter, painter, and in various other trades\u2014he gained first-hand experience in every aspect of construction. This journey shaped a deep understanding of the building process and a commitment to hard work and integrity.<\/p><p>After earning a General Contractor license in Massachusetts, Rebbert de Oliveira began leading both residential and commercial projects. While experienced in many areas of construction, his true passion lies in residential work. Each home is treated with the same care and dedication as if it were his own, ensuring every detail delivers quality, functionality, and personality.<\/p><p>Today, our company blends Rebbert\u2019s personal journey with professional expertise. We don\u2019t just build structures\u2014we create spaces where families can live, grow, and feel at home.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-08c7d21 exad-sticky-section-no exad-glass-effect-no elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"08c7d21\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>Address<\/b>: 52 Bailey St, Lynn\u00a0 &#8211; Massachusetts 01904 &#8211; United States<br \/><b>Phone<\/b>: +17815201982<br \/><b>Email<\/b>: rebbert@jrhcontructions.com<br \/><b>Opening Hours: <\/b>Monday to Saturday 7am &#8211; 6pm<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-67f499cd exad-sticky-section-no exad-glass-effect-no elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"67f499